{
  "_comment": "Author your own Urfael personas. Copy this to ~/Urfael-memory/personas.json (the git-versioned memory repo, so each persona is auditable + revertible). A persona is a VOICE overlay only — same tools, same model routing, same vault, same sandbox; only the stance/advice-shape differs. Urfael force-appends an immutable safety clause at spawn, so a persona can NEVER relax the moat. Switch with `urfael persona <id>` or just say 'become the privateer' in chat. The five built-ins (architect, sage, operator, muse, analyst) plus 'urfael' (the anchor) are always present and cannot be shadowed.",
